I dont believe the first answer is correct as ContosoPF is a PF mailbox, not a PF

Second answer is correct:
Get-PublicFolderitemStatistics -Identity “name of PF” | where {$_.hasattachments -eq $true}
Get-PublicFolderitemStatistics -Identity “name of PF” | where {$_.hasattachments -eq $false}
